items.Video_Title: Dudes When They Get Their First Essentials Hoodie ...
items.Video_Description:
Essentials hoodies do be super comfy tho LMAO

I LOVE YA'LL HOPE YOU ENJOY AND ARE MOTIVATED TO GO CHASE YOUR OWN BAG!!! All love :)


Get started with your own business 
Make a instagram reselling account

Summer is coming up it’s a perfect time to start reselling sneakers
 
First things you will need is a logo, good pictures/listing  and a reference post.

A logo you can literally pay someone a side gig website like fiver to make a website, i made my first logo by myself i used this website called canva, not sponsored and you guys can experiment and learn how to make your own logo 

Good pictures/listing you want to make sure your pictures have good lighting and shows the best features of the shoes

Lace up the laces
Take off the little rocks of the soles

Little details like that go a long way and can be the tipping point for potential customers  

A reference post

A reference post is a post where people who have done business with you can comment on the post and detail how the transaction went with you
This is important because the more positive reviews you get the more trustworthy you are 

Do NOT fake refs, do not ask random people to comment that you’ve done good business if you didn’t, it wont work out and people that might leave those refs might be scammers and the  you can be labeled as a scammer.

Connections are so important the most important 

Where to find deals

Because connections provide knowledge, the world i s abundant with resources and money that every can make, with connections you can be info that can help you make thousands 


Always REMAIN ACTIVE, try to post on you ig story at least once a day if you can


Whether its providing a update to your followers and reposting a funny sneaker related meme


BEWARE OF SCAMMERS
There are a lot of scammers starting off, usually when you are first starting off they will target you. They will seem very interested in your item and won't even negotiate. And then they will usually ask you for your email to be able to send you the money but the reason that they need your email is to send a fake email from the payment company like paypal, saying the sent you the money.



Make sure ya'll like, comment, and subscribe! If you guys have any questions drop them below in the comments!

items.Video_Title: ABERCROMBIE CLOTHING IN 2022 Try On HAUL! How To Style Abercrombie & Fitch Essentials
items.Video_Description:
Here's a Clothing Haul featuring my newest pickups from Abercrombie and Fitch... Not something I thought I'd be saying in 2022! But the Hype is back. A&F has completely rebranded, changed their designs and is targeting more streetwear, sneakerhead and casual consumers. There's pro's and con's in this Abercrombie review, but they did a great job with their new clothing offering, considering they're an affordable Mall Brand and are similar to american eagle and GAP as you'll see with the clothes I bought. We've got sweaters, cardigans, flannels, sweatshirts and outerwear coats.... I skipped the denim, hoodies, tee's and puffer jackets.. but I'll buy them next time. It's a mix of basic essentials and trendy graphics, my kinda style. Be sure to hit that THUMBS UP if you enjoyed this Abercrombie & Fitch Clothing haul!
